        public SyncOptions.SyncOptionsBuilder matchAllInclusionFilters(boolean b)
        Sets matchAllInclusionFilters flag. If set to true, the file will be included only if ALL inclusion filters match. If set to false, the file will be included if ANY ONE of the inclusion filters match.
        Parameters:
